        h1 Relevant Research
        ul.resources-list
          li
            a(href='https://sflc.in/sc-judgment-safeguards-shutdown-limited-relief-kashmir', target='_blank')
              strong  Legal Analysis of SC judgement on communication blockade in Kashmir: 
